casebody.data:
City of Cuyahoga Falls, Appellee, v. Ashcraft et al., Appellants.

[Cite as Cuyahoga Falls v. Ashcraft (1990), 52 Ohio St. 3d 602.]

(No. 89-936 Submitted May 5, 1990 Decided June 27, 1990.) Virgil Arrington, Jr., deputy law director, for appellee. Weick, Gibson & Lowry, Kenneth L. Gibson and Leslie S. Graske, for appellants.

This appeal is dismissed, sua sponte, as having been improvidently allowed.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes, Wright, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., concur. Douglas, J., dissents.
